com.twitterapime.model
Class MetadataSet

java.lang.Object
  com.twitterapime.model.MetadataSet

public final class MetadataSet
extends java.lang.Object

MetadataSet is a interface that specifies a collection of metadata attributes applicable to the entities that implement the interface Entity. The prefix of each constant indicates which class that constant belongs to. For instance, "TWEET_XXX" belongs to Tweet class.

Since:
1.0
Version:
1.8
Author:
Ernandes Mourao Junior (ernandes@gmail.com)

USERACCOUNT_PICTURE_URI_MINI

public static final java.lang.String USERACCOUNT_PICTURE_URI_MINI

Report the user account's picture URI mini (24px by 24px), e.g., "http://api.twitter.com/1/users/profile_image/username.json?size=mini".

This URI does not return any image, but instead returns a 302 redirect to the actual image resource.
